        <blockquote class="text-lg text-neutral-700 italic mb-4">
          "iFixx fixed our bathroom leak within hours of calling. Professional, clean, and fairly priced. They're now our go-to for everything."
        </blockquote>
        <p class="text-sm font-bold text-neutral-900">‚Äî Charlotte Homeowner</p>
